|timeline=Circa [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]]<ref name="Date">The [[Roleplaying game|roleplaying]] adventure ''[[Child of Light]]'' is set four [[Standard month/Legends|months]] after the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]], an event that is dated by ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'' to the sixth month of the [[Standard year/Legends|year]] [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]]. As the ''Atlas'' states that there are twelve months in the [[Galactic Standard Calendar]], it can therefore be inferred that ''Child of Light'' takes place in the tenth month of 3 ABY. The adventure [[Soulsaber (adventure)|''Soulsaber'']] is set approximately four months after ''Child of Light'' and can thus be dated to the second month of [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]]. ''Light and Dark'' is set just over three years after ''Soulsaber'' and is therefore placed in around [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]].</ref>
